52	/** Functions that use plug-ins (external) dictionaries_loader.
53	  *
54	  * Get the value of the attribute of the specified type.
55	  *     dictGetType(dictionary, attribute, id),
56	  *         Type - placeholder for the type name, any numeric and string types are currently supported.
57	  *        The type must match the actual attribute type with which it was declared in the dictionary structure.
58	  *
59	  * Get an array of identifiers, consisting of the source and parents chain.
60	  *  dictGetHierarchy(dictionary, id).
61	  *
62	  * Is the first identifier the child of the second.
63	  *  dictIsIn(dictionary, child_id, parent_id).
